com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.reactor

Class ReactorErrorInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.reactor.ReactorErrorInfo

  • public class ReactorErrorInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    ErrorInfo is used by various Reactor methods to return error or warning information to the user. If the code is SUCCESS, then there is no error. Otherwise, the user should inspect the code, Error and location.
    See Also:
    Error
